<div class="container">

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Booking Details</h2>
    <p>Duration: <%= @booking.start_date %> to  <%= @booking.end_date %> | Booking # <%= @booking.id %></p>
    <div class="box">
      <div class="row div">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <h3>Service Details</h3>
          <p><%= @booking.service.name %></p>
          <img src="http://www.pitivi.org/i/pitivi-icon-256.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <h3>Customer Notes</h3>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras fermentum et nisi vitae rutrum. Quisque a augue imperdiet, ullamcorper turpis et, fringilla purus. Fusce ut faucibus erat. Vestibulum sed massa in libero ultrices malesuada ut nec diam. Praesent posuere faucibus molestie. Vestibulum ac elit nec ligula varius pulvinar et ut ipsum. Fusce pharetra vel nunc ac laoreet.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <h3>Status</h3>
          <h4 style="color: green;">Accepted</h4>
          <div id="status-change">
            <h3>Change Status</h3>
            <select name="" id="">
              <option value="Pending">Pending</option>
              <option value="Accepted">Accepted</option>
              <option value="Awaiting Payment">Awaiting Payment</option>
              <option value="In Progress">In Progress</option>
              <option value="Completed">Completed</option>
              <option value="Declined">Declined</option>
            </select>
            <%= link_to 'Update booking', vendor_service_path(@booking.service), class:"btn btn-success" %>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <h3>Client Details:</h3>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li>
              <%= @booking.user.first_name %>
              <%= @booking.user.last_name %>
            </li>
            <li><%= @booking.user.email %></li>
            <li><%= @booking.user.phone_number %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <h3>Payment Method</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><img src="https://images-eu.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/02/checkout/payselect/card-logos-small/visa._CB196106848_.gif" alt=""> ****1234 </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <h3>Booking Summary</h3>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p>Start:</p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p><%= @booking.start_date %></p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p>End:</p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p><%= @booking.end_date %></p> </div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p>Duration:</p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p><%= (@booking.end_date - @booking.start_date).to_i %> day(s)</p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p>Daily Rate:</p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p>£<%= number_with_precision(@booking.service.daily_rate, precision: 2) %></p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p>Total: </p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-6"><p>£<%= number_with_precision(@booking.total_cost, precision: 2) %></p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <%= link_to 'Back to all bookings', vendor_bookings_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




